    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=nprwgafri4]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nprwgafri4]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=sqhh28yskx]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=sqhh28yskx]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=u942bn7szv]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=u942bn7szv]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757676129508&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757676129508&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"596967460\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"94fed18d-f9b2-4c24-b2b8-be42393b27a8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757676129508&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757676129508&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"sqhh28yskx\">Project</span></strong>: The Smoking Gnome</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"u942bn7szv\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>:  R&eacute;mi Perrier</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"nprwgafri4\">Edited by:</span></strong> Leif Pedersen</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/resources/The_Smoking_Gnome/The_Smoking_Gnome_RfM.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757678439483&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757678439483&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597000253\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"046122a8-1b0a-47f7-9869-9aa45fa8cbd9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757678439483&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757678439483&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><p>The Smoking Gnome is a creation of artist <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.remi3d.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">R&eacute;mi Perrier</a> and originated as a school exercise supervised by <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/baptiste-lebouc-44969853\" rel=\"nofollow\">Baptiste Lebouc</a>, where students had to choose a fictional character. R&eacute;mi's ambition was to bring to life an interesting character, with a look that was both enigmatic and captivating, using intentional lighting to emphasize his mysterious personality.</p><p>The RenderMan for Maya project was edited by Pixar's <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://leif3d.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Leif Pedersen</a> to adhere to Pixar-standard rendering practices.</p><p /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"full-width\" data-local-id=\"30f03dee-7bc7-4170-9e17-da89bddd118b\" data-macro-id=\"ef6533aa296ea662a66ad95e4dced8d88be9070271ac4783b18466c144bb5f74\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"1080\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1072645231\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"1080\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p /><p>For texturing, I worked with <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://texturing.xyz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Texturing XYZ's</a> Multi-Channel textures to capture maximum details in the skin. Using ACES color management proved crucial, as it allowed me to integrate physical values into the shading and enhance the realism of the lighting. The lighting studio, included with this project download, is ideal to calibrate the shading without chromatic interference, guaranteeing lighting fidelity.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-aovs.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-aovs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675536008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=243\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/smoking-gnome-aovs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675536008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"1686\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597000215\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-aovs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"3948126a-6e4a-46e4-a54e-088f06fafefa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-aovs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675536008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=486 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-aovs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675536008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=243 1x\" /></span><p /><p>This project taught me a lot, especially about the importance of physical research. I learned a great deal about creating an eye and its specific refraction values, which helped me refine my rendering and make my character more believable.<br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-closeup-eyes.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-eyes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675565947&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-eyes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675565947&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597000221\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-closeup-eyes.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"a04b1b44-03b9-4368-a4e6-eec804db2a2f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-eyes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675565947&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-eyes.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675565947&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-closeup-lips.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-lips.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757675576844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-lips.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757675576844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597098500\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-closeup-lips.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"1f74bc1c-68d8-4f06-b96c-87afe04c7bb4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-lips.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757675576844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-closeup-lips.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757675576844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p /><p>I drew color inspiration from Rembrandt&rsquo;s use of chiaroscuro, particularly in paintings like <em>Philosopher in Meditation</em> and <em>The Holy Family</em>, to enhance the mystery and depth of my character. In one of the lighting rigs, I also played with Shatner Lighting, which always brings out the film noir drama!</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-mood-board.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-mood-board.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675604812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=273\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/smoking-gnome-mood-board.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675604812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"691\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597393409\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-mood-board.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"b9ef0d36-cba5-4eed-87eb-ab7d185ee67a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-mood-board.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675604812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=546 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/smoking-gnome-mood-board.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675604812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=273 1x\" /></span><p /><p>The Smoking Gnome is an excellent opportunity for users to dissect a RenderMan-centric project, designed to take advantage of interactive workflows in RenderMan XPU. Play with the project, create some interesting lighting, and have fun!</p><p /><hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"TheSmokingGnome-AbouttheArtist\">About the Artist</h3><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.remi3d.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"remi-perrier-headshot.png\" width=\"208\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/remi-perrier-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675672117&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=208&amp;height=208\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/remi-perrier-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675672117&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"596967453\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"remi-perrier-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"c29e534a-ae7f-4009-a802-11521edff262\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/remi-perrier-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675672117&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=416&amp;height=416 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/remi-perrier-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675672117&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=208&amp;height=208 1x\" /></span></a><p>R&eacute;mi has always been fascinated by animation and CGI, particularly in bringing characters to life, a passion nurtured in him from an early age by his parents. Currently a student at ESMA in Lyon, France, he&rsquo;s looking to work in Lighting and Surfacing. &quot;My dream is to inspire people and make them dream the way other artists have inspired me.&quot;</p><hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"ef8cec14-5cf7-4818-ae6d-fee8db02cd01\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"TheSmokingGnome-Attribution-NonCommercial4.0International(CCBY-NC4.0)\">Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)</h3></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"by-nc.png\" width=\"97\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675755658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=97&amp;height=33\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675755658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"34\" data-width=\"97\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"596934669\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"by-nc.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"fbb91605-eb07-4ee9-861f-0da8f629d88d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675755658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=194&amp;height=66 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/by-nc.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757675755658&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=97&amp;height=33 1x\" /></span><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757677574014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/596770821/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757677574014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597065736\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"596770821\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"04baf7cb-3116-4c05-bebb-d5eec8f0ac13\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757677574014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/596770821/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757677574014&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
